{"tid":968102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5日內第二宗！台海灘再現豬屍　疑從陸海漂上岸","createTime":"2019-01-04T03:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T07:06:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"070175bbd07b1d047e07a843b0b2fc76d026e775","tid":968102,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"台灣海巡署長李仲威披露，繼周一（12月31日）金門縣金沙鎮海岸之後，周五（1月4日）上午8時40分在烏坵鄉小坵島海灘，再度發現一隻死豬，並指小坵島上沒有養豬場，明顯是從中國大陸海漂上岸。 <br />\n<br />\n李仲威在上午舉行的「非洲豬瘟中央災害應變中心第2次會議」作出上述表示。他又指，已請金門的防疫人員做後續處理，發現死豬的地點目前已拉起封鎖線，有待檢驗死豬身上是否染有非洲豬瘟。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190104/bkn-20190104111050375-0104_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190104%2Fbkn-20190104111050375-0104_00952_001.html&d=vzqZYnDb1ywAalcEFxHNhUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c8050000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190104/bkn-20190104111050375-0104_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b15782f72962fb318b72d8d4aa74ea092611f440","tid":968102,"uid":20937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又送禮"},{"pid":"45400b553b183377a045407d04aaabd5d1471dbf","tid":968102,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c112b6c16fbe8eae25052c6ac4f23564ee3956f","tid":968102,"uid":182933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d799d0c3eca38f181b20c834337ce2f750d6ea8","tid":968102,"uid":39277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"生化襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji